  "detailed_description": "<strong>START AS A MINER, BECOME A FIGHTER</strong><br><br>Asteroidle is an idle game that allows you to asteroid mining. Discover technologies, buy and upgrade them. Travel at space continuously and face with new challenges.<br><br>• Limitless Offline Progress<br>• 100 achievements (in game over 500+ achievements)<br>• Over 500+ upgrades<br>• 20+ technologies<br>• 15 different space objects<br>• 2 Bosses<br>• Daily Quests and Challenges<br>• Travel between sectors, discover new galaxies<br>• Jump to dimensions, discover deep space<br>• Build your own Fleet<br>• Send your licensed pilots to missions<br>• Obtain new skills and surpass yourself<br>• Be the most dangerous person in space  (Leaderboard)<br>• 2 mini games<br><br><strong>NOTE: Trailer is outdated, it belongs to first release. A lot of  changes happened and new features added since first release, I'll update it asap.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2007080/extras/2959a4658c29d33db8288eea5be1ff12.poster.avif?t=1678550855\" width=320 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2007080/extras/2959a4658c29d33db8288eea5be1ff12.webm?t=1678550855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2007080/extras/2959a4658c29d33db8288eea5be1ff12.mp4?t=1678550855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>START AS A MINER, BECOME A FIGHTER</strong><br><br>Asteroidle is an idle game that allows you to asteroid mining. Discover technologies, buy and upgrade them. Travel at space continuously and face with new challenges.<br><br>• Limitless Offline Progress<br>• 100 achievements (in game over 500+ achievements)<br>• Over 500+ upgrades<br>• 20+ technologies<br>• 15 different space objects<br>• 2 Bosses<br>• Daily Quests and Challenges<br>• Travel between sectors, discover new galaxies<br>• Jump to dimensions, discover deep space<br>• Build your own Fleet<br>• Send your licensed pilots to missions<br>• Obtain new skills and surpass yourself<br>• Be the most dangerous person in space  (Leaderboard)<br>• 2 mini games<br><br><strong>NOTE: Trailer is outdated, it belongs to first release. A lot of  changes happened and new features added since first release, I'll update it asap.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2007080/extras/2959a4658c29d33db8288eea5be1ff12.poster.avif?t=1678550855\" width=320 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2007080/extras/2959a4658c29d33db8288eea5be1ff12.webm?t=1678550855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2007080/extras/2959a4658c29d33db8288eea5be1ff12.mp4?t=1678550855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
